      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been super meticulous with the maintenance, so it runs like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been truly loved and pampered, this is definitely the one. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
