    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a showroom-quality E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. This specimen features the S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system for instantaneous throttle response. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. This vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and proactive rear subframe reinforcement. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and factory-spec dampers, ensuring original suspension geometry. Finished in collector-grade condition with flawless paint depth and an interior free of bolster wear or pixel degradation, this is a turn-key example for the purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
