    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This garage-kept masterpiece retains its original, deep-gloss factory paint, recently treated with a professional-grade ceramic coating to ensure a mirror-like finish free of any swirl marks, door dings, or stone chips. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of pristine leather and flawless trim; the seats show zero bolster wear, and the original floor mats are included. Every electronic component, from the premium surround-sound system to the dual-zone climate control, functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been maintained exclusively by brand-certified technicians with a comprehensive, paper-documented service history included in the sale. Recent preventative maintenance includes a full synthetic oil service and a fresh set of high-performance tires with less than 500 miles on them. With only one meticulous owner, this vehicle has never been exposed to harsh weather, smoke, or pets. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a 'time capsule' vehicle in showroom condition.",
